title: Jurassic Realm
description: Explore a lost world in search of dinosaurs in this adventurous puzzler. Search for hidden dinosaur images and discover the legendary T.Rex in Quest mode. Unlock even more dinosaur images in the challenging Arcade mode. Choose your own path from a huge map with a variety of travel options. Featuring more than 150 challenging levels, 19 dinosaurs to discover, and hours of addictive family fun, unearth Jurassic Realm today
